adingError(exception);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static void rethrowUnlessNativeImageDynamicClassLoadingError(Throwable throwable) throws Throwable {\n        if (hasNativeImageUnsupportedFeatureError(throwable)) {\n            return;\n        }\n        throw throwable;\n    }\n\n    private static boolean hasNativeImageUnsupportedFeatureError(Throwable throwable) {\n        Throwable current = throwable;\n        while (current != null) {\n            if (current instanceof Error error && NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            current = current.getCause();\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n}\n"}
[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering method keys**\n\nI'm figuring out that I need a MethodWrapper to create a key based on the method name, parameters, and return type. For testing, I can use class.getMethod since it’s public. I’m also pondering whether I should use an interface for this, so I can clearly define the method signatures. Identifying equal keys is another important aspect to make sure everything matches up correctly. I want to ensure I handle this process smoothly!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0d09153518c040920169fa6c9584f08190a7d190fd0f51df72\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-myihm1JxE7176eZVhyi3-rfHorKBRZYw40hZzeKBgUMRJp-p2xmKzQPlTl3rk765eL61xLrWN7R2-o7AXXtUrXfl9_oXFrTfJMQQW22trsVN8j3eE8_ULFpfEGVPl_rTmyfdWbSkRBT7Ttw8ewgtr8KBV9c3yeQWDz9m8OlEXCc22TzVNSO4hagztK95ne5f5PMPFiNUa8SMN_huX-0cjYirB8Iw7DguLJFKWl_M3PGB342ZAyWjrZNQmvCCmNMKH1LAU5BVq1Ia1jWr4ofp2J9ma-8A7Jc2yUg--492yzsA8nE6Iy5m4PY4r8JC2B8QqKSz1hHw2zU_6pzgvDPCV8q3ftPVVE8oc9ywdXTNQc5RnI6aE97trHHGhDQTrIUITBgwrBGuLaicLon0P5OfldBn-Dn_BkNTvXdDZzYFRa4a-p8EGlCtuH8QsZiiusrvTu1rG8x2R9QRVuQIlANZ1Us0N9qdRoReoqnVtsg9QyTvX7hsR39IzGZy24iT96UhN9Q8jWOAa3Zj2PV1SjHWoMp6rSrA9zorYT6zgXGBVxttjE7p1V7UNderlrUGRiI6yZzqmX1jHMQ3SchdHEvDNE7lWFw1VIk2dAiSe655Ity2D_V-rxxBTRhZq4bo2D_3fTnakeH4zAruw4cqlp_KpPXZtV7M483Cx_N77O5wHf0IX-SWUHsv_WDC5ltmfjvn9P2_dPXGqk1zwlTnBYQBDEHMAXbDZUzf9KnL0RGV94RupNY9W1-v53opvoSFCiIPecYvFqyb8iE29eEoMN7OtMlsNi1d1N8gB2UmxH-Y-gk11rXIdhu9UQUnicTFm8acpfxdayknKL7wmMzcL-L6SygWcd-wQst1V90HiN_bvL27SM97qT5GW-YnAOKZWcirLPyQ8ENg9MFn926oryPDGjbnl_ph4NLZKKuKoftC47A4zZ2CDzrHtsltHKGyMNjnjzUokyPafz1QQHoreqhEbg5yJZnr_7XWZCHSwnck0O3C0D1PDaey6fmuHW5W6GX4aCy_8IB74YNIFPX0whDQxrro-JB1mLo2ivG-LHsj9rWrFl3xSz2VNkjGORacWK0dcdI_ylOdSMFDLUtzrocP41JPvaPRImNNVdPg25lIqpvqYatB5qj43jx4wrqLcO4gMmQxdJT-yRBhtXe_yF_49MtaZyxnfRN2Ji1nJLLKh8__3jGFzu7vtO2E23eeMARHcarXTtPJDeOSGXWsWOMvjPHAojpCB95uP_Pgc4QPz2ApUU2o0D7FPJxIisYjEkCiSRU